EVENT & LARGE PARTY FORM
REQUEST AN EVENT
Excited to plan a special occasion? Whether it's a birthday, baby shower, corporate event, or any joyful gathering, fill out the form below!
We’re ready to secure your preferred date and tailor every detail to make your celebration unforgettable and a huge success!
Reservations for parties of 16 guests or fewer can be made by clicking the button below.
CLICK HERE
For all inquiries of parties with 17 or more guests, please fill out the form below and we’ll be in touch soon.
Notice: JavaScript is required for this content.
That data is being printed as a workaround to page builders reordering the order of the scripts loaded
OUR VENUE
INTERIOR | BREEZEWAY
We have an intimate interior capable of hosting 37 people. The modern design features custom fixtures from local artists and handmade wood tables and bar.
We also have breezeway seating available in a climate-controlled environment with mood lighting. Seating may be rearranged to accommodate your party.
